text.default: 21. Does this participant have bed bugs in his/her house?

text.sw: 21. Je, mshiriki huyu ana kunguni katika nyumba yake?

text.default: 22. Has this participant recently passed worms in the stool in the last 15 days?
text.pt: 22. O participante teve parasitas nas fezes nos últimos 15 dias?
text.sw: 22. Je, mshiriki huyu alitoa kinyesi chenye minyoo hivi karibuni katika siku 15 zilizopita?

text.sw: 25. Mshiriki huyu kwa sasa ni mjamzito?

text.default: [If yes] 25a. Is this participant taking Intermittent Preventive Treatment (IPTp) for malaria?

text.sw: [Ikiwa ndio] 25a. Mshiriki huyu anatumia dozi ya kuzuia malaria wakati wa ujauzito (IPTp)?

text.default: 26a. [If yes] How many people shared the net?

text.sw: 26a. [Ikiwa ndiyo] Ni watu wangapi walio lala kwenye chandarua hicho?

text.default: 28. At what time does this participant usually go to bed?

text.pt: 30. A que horas é que este participante costuma acordar?
text.sw: 30. Mshiriki huyu kwa kawaida huamka saa ngapi?

text.default: 31. At what time does this participant usually go outside?

text.default: 32a. [If yes] Has this participant ever travelled to any of these countries?

text.sw: 32a. [Ikiwa ndiyo] Mshiriki huyu amewahi kusafiri kwa yoyote kati ya nchi hizi?

text.default: 33. Does this participant regularly travel or sleep outside of the home during the first part of the year? (January-June)
text.pt: 33. O participante viaja regularmente ou dorme fora de casa durante a primeira parte do ano? (Janeiro-Junho)

text.default: 33a. If yes, how many different trips does this participant have during the first part of the year?
text.pt: 33a. Se sim, quantas viagens diferentes é que o participante faz durante a primeira parte do ano?
text.sw: 33a. Ikiwa ndiyo, ni safari ngapi tofauti ambazo mshiriki huyu anazo wakati wa sehemu ya kwanza ya mwaka?
